# YOLO format labels: [class_id] [x_center] [y_center] [width] [height]
# All values normalized to [0, 1] relative to image dimensions.
#
# CRITICAL FOR SMALL OBJECTS:
# Bounding boxes must be EXTREMELY TIGHT — any background pixels
# inside the box act as noise at the micro-object scale.
#
# Example (drone at center of image, tiny):
#   0 0.5123 0.3456 0.0234 0.0189
